mksinterface.mksitem.src

Class Mksinterface_mksitem

  • java.lang.Object
    • mksinterface.mksitem.src.Mksinterface_mksitem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Mksinterface_mksitem_changeOrConcern, Mksinterface_mksitem_developmentOrder, Mksinterface_mksitem_project, Mksinterface_mksitem_release, Mksinterface_mksitem_requirement, Mksinterface_mksitem_requirementDocument, Mksinterface_mksitem_task

    public abstract class Mksinterface_mksitem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the base of every item in integrity. It is an abstract class, so it couldn't be created without defining a special type of the item. All basic methods are implemented to access the item and all methods which are the same in all items INFO: Please be careful by using addFields, the fields to add will not be checked if they are correct and possible because there is too much runtime loss
    Author:
    ckaltenboeck
